===Etymology===
From [[Brät]] + [[Wurst]]. The folk etymological derivation from [[braten]] + [[Wurst]] is incorrect.

===Noun===
'''Bratwurst''' ''f'' (nominative plural '''Bratwürste''')

# a [[bratwurst]]
#:''Zum Abendessen gab es gestern '''Bratwurst'''.''

